reference:
  Pspell Functions
  Pspell





    &reftitle.intro;


     These functions allow you to check the spelling of a word and offer
     suggestions.

    &note.no-windows.extension;




    &reftitle.required;


     To compile PHP with pspell support, you need the aspell library, 
     available from &url.aspell;.



